Module chav1961.purelib

Package chav1961.purelib.model

This package contains an API to use with models. Model is a container with ContentMetadataInterface type. It contains a tree of ContentNodeMetadata nodes. Every node describes an entity in the model. This package has a set of classes to manage this model at the runtime:

  • SimpleContentMetadata class, implemented ContentMetadataInterface
  • MutableContentNodeMetadata class, implemented ContentNodeMetadata
  • ContentModelFactory class to load model from external or to build model by existent entities
  • FieldFormat class to describe format associated with the model entity
  • ModelUtils utility class contains set of useful methods to manipulate with models

Model and it's API is a base for almost all the Pure Library infrastructure.
